      "role": "user",
      "content": "but wind doesn't explain the rhythm. it's too specific. the way they break formation right before the gust hits... it's like they're relaying a sequence. i've been watching them for weeks and it's not random. i can basically sense when the transition is about to happen because of how they signal to each other. it's almost like a language.",
